      "note": "SAT files start with 'ACIS ' or 'ACIS_SAT ' or a version integer (400, 700, 1600, etc.). The exact first token varies by ACIS version and creating application. Look for 'End-of-ACIS-data' near end of file to confirm."
    }
  },
  "variables": {
    "satHeader": "",
